The tracking results of randomly selected centrosome movies starting at different cell stages were analysed.
@BULLET Chimera track. The track contains more than one centrosome or non-centrosome object and it is not a long or fused track.
@BULLET Missing track. A centrosome is not tracked at all.
@BULLET Particle track. A non-centrosome object is tracked but involves no centrosomes.
